My husband and I went to Patisserie Manon for lunch based on the Yelp reviews.
We recently moved to Vegas from Washington, DC and were looking for an authentic French pastry shop/cafe, similar to our favourite one in Georgetown, where we could get a Croque Monsieur/Madame.
