" Then he crouched down and pulled out the tray, eyeing them apprehensively.
Had my craving for escargot not been overwhelming, I likely would have cancelled my order and left.
As it is, the order was tasty and I feel just fine.
And I'll probably eat it again.
But someone needs to have a chat with male staff for this company... see my review for other location for more info.

